criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of Chronic Heart Failure;

          -  low health status.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cognitive/psychiatric impairment (inability to complete questionnaires);

          -  nursing home resident;

          -  irreversible non-cardiac medical condition likely to affect 6-month survival or
             ability to execute study protocol;

          -  prior heart transplantation.
